cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.CL 

The paper deals with computer-assisted teaching with explanations, which involves machine learning and computer vision techniques to generate visual explanations. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper also involves human learners, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
